   <narrative xml:lang="EN">RECLAIM Sustainability! Egypt-Cotton &amp; Textiles</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to:
-Regulate frameworks in Egypt that contribute to sustainable and inclusive international value chains.
-Improve gender responsive workplace policies and practices in Egypt.
-Facilitate Smallholder cotton farmers and textile workers to negotiate with buyers fair value, better and safe working conditions, and environmental practices.
-Design digital tools for the benefit of cotton and textile producers in Egypt or make use and develop current systems and apps.</narrative>
